metadata.name: RP Music Key #1
metadata.description:
The Rap Pack just got bigger, and just in time for our first musical adventure! 
This token is verifiable for the following incentives:
- Free Mint for future music NFT drops w/ streaming royalties
- Perpetual entry into a drawing for royalty share on all future mints
- Access to Key Holder Metaverse performances and events 
- Access to future physical performances
- More benefits will be unlocked as we move forward on our musical journey
[Review your traits for any airdrops attached to your token]
